<item>
            <title>[LU-19248] sanity-lnet: Failed to add net tcp on if test1pg</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19248</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Chris Horn &amp;lt;chris.horn@hpe.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6eb3e86a-5f9c-4c4a-a434-7b21d1b61882&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6eb3e86a-5f9c-4c4a-a434-7b21d1b61882&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_107 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Failed to add net tcp on if test1pg
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/115643&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/115643&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-553.58.1.el8_10.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/115643&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/115643&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-553.58.1.el8_lustre.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;2e49bc7dd1 &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18812&quot; title=&quot;lnet: restrict IP addresses that socklnd listens on&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-18812&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-18812&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; lnet: restrict IP addresses that socklnd listens on&lt;/tt&gt; seems to cause test failures with ipv6&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;looking at test_107:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;00000400:00020000:0.0:1754666665.160317:0:63460:0:(lib-socket.c:317:lnet_sock_create()) Error trying to bind to 2001:db8:0:f101::1/7988: rc = -99
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I can reproduce locally with master. If I revert &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18812&quot; title=&quot;lnet: restrict IP addresses that socklnd listens on&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-18812&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-18812&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; then the test passes&lt;/p&gt;







&lt;p&gt;VVVVVVV DO NOT REMOVE LINES BELOW, Added by Maloo for auto-association VVVVVVV&lt;br/&gt;
sanity-lnet test_107 - Failed to add net tcp on if test1pg&lt;br/&gt;
sanity-lnet test_109 - Failed to add net tcp on if test1pg&lt;br/&gt;
sanity-lnet test_200 - Failed to configure LNet in non-default namespace rc = 156&lt;br/&gt;
sanity-lnet test_201 - Failed to configure LNet in non-default namespace rc = 156&lt;br/&gt;
sanity-lnet test_203 - Failed to add net in non-default namespace&lt;/p&gt;</description>
